posting_body: ['Modera San Pedro Square', 'Property Address', '28 N Almaden Avenue, ,', 'San Jose, CA, 95110', '<URL>', 'Floor Plan Details', 'Name: A06', '1 Bedrooms / 1 Bathrooms', '728-734 Sq.', 'Ft.', '$3,467.00 - $3,666.00', 'Community Amenities', 'State-of-the-art 24 hour fitness and yoga studio', 'Automated parcel system and 24/7 pick up', 'Game room and TV lounge', 'Co-working lounge spaces', 'Fireside lounges', 'Outdoor terrace, furnished with lounging areas and outdoor kitchens', 'Bike friendly, with on site bike storage and repair', 'Do-it-yourself (DIY) room', 'Pet friendly, with on site pet spa', 'Walking distance to Diridon Station (connection to Caltrain, Amtrak and corporate tech buses)', 'Located in the heart of San Pedro Square historic district', 'Bicycle repair station', 'Accepts Electronic Payments', 'Near Transit and Walk Score of 93!', 'Pet Policy', 'We love your furry companions and welcome up to two per apartment home.', 'While we are huge fans of individuality (and the exotic), we have to ask that exotic pals, such as skunks and ferrets, find happy homes with a friend or family member.', 'Please note that we reserve the right to disallow certain aggressive breeds of dogs and aquariums as per our pet addendum.', 'Please contact our leasing office for information.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday - Friday 10:00 A.M. - 6:00 P.M.', 'Saturday 10:00 A.M. - 5:00 P.M.', 'Property Contact', 'show contact info', 'ADA ACCESSIBLE', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '*Photos May Not Be OF Exact Home Available']
